cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

The paper deals with domain adaptation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed method involves self-supervised learning, which is a popular technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The experiments are conducted on image datasets, which are commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) research.
